suhunya membekukan...

389
00:30:57,960 --> 00:31:02,120
...sementara menunggu mesin
kursi lift ini dihidupkan kembali.

390
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:37,960
Kami di atas sini!

391
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:41,480
- Tolong!
- Tolong kami!

392
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:43,680
- Kembalikan penahan itu ke posisinya.
- Tolong!

393
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,400
Kembalikan penahan
itu ke posisinya, Joe!

394
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:50,600
Astaga, dinginnya
menusuk tulang!

395
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:37,680
- Tolong!
- Kami di sini!

396
00:32:44,280 --> 00:32:49,400
- Di atas sini!
- Tolong kami!

397
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:53,520
Cody, ini pangkalan.

398
00:32:57,400 --> 00:33:01,600
