408
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:59,960
- Kembali!
- Tidak!

409
00:34:08,240 --> 00:34:10,520
Hei, kembali!

410
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:18,040
Astaga. Tidak.

411
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:22,280
Tidak!

412
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:45,840
- Wajahku pedih.
- Mesinnya segara dihidupkan kembali.

413
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:48,960
- Tidak mungkin.
- Harus!

414
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,320
Ada yang tahu jam
berapa sekarang?

415
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:56,640
Sebentar, aku kembali ke loker
dulu ya, aku akan cek di ponselku.

416
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:04,560
Tiga cereal utama
sepanjang hari.

417
