553
00:47:32,600 --> 00:47:34,480
Baik.

554
00:47:36,560 --> 00:47:38,800
Aku pasti bisa.

555
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:46,320
Aku memegangimu.

556
00:47:46,320 --> 00:47:49,040
Sial.

557
00:47:49,040 --> 00:47:51,040
Jangan melihat ke bawah.

