00:47:56,800 --> 00:47:59,040
Sepatu botku terlalu berat.

559
00:48:13,360 --> 00:48:16,040
Sarung tanganku
terpotong oleh kabel.

560
00:48:19,640 --> 00:48:21,560
Kau bisa meraihnya?

561
00:48:30,280 --> 00:48:32,840
