572
00:49:36,720 --> 00:49:40,880
Dan!

573
00:50:03,520 --> 00:50:08,520
Jangan dengarkan.

574
00:50:15,440 --> 00:50:18,160
Baiklah.

575
00:50:55,200 --> 00:50:57,960
Tidak!

576
00:51:25,400 --> 00:51:27,960
Sarung tanganku terpotong kabel.

